    "Prefer bento gap tokens over tw-mb-4/tw-gap-4 on migrated routes (see tokenCompliance.test.ts)",
    "Prefer server-side Firestore queries where indexed",
    "80-line function guideline for new code"
  ],
  "ui_tokens": {
    "dominant": "#0f172a",
    "structural_border": "#334155",
    "accent_gold": "#fbbf24",
    "player_os_corners": "clip-path chamfer — not border-radius",
